构造方法详细信息

ScheduleQueue

public ScheduleQueue(int size,
                     int lowestPrid)
Init a queue

参数：
size - the capacity of the queue,not a precision value,if queue size exceed this value, workers which add jobs should wait
lowestPrid - the lowest priority which worker thread hold,the default priority is range from 1 to 10,reverse from java thread priority
